{
  "description": "A wide-angle, high-angle view of an industrial port city bathed in the golden light of either sunrise or sunset. The scene is dominated by a large body of water with a long pier or bridge extending into it, connecting to industrial facilities and warehouses on the distant shore. The facilities include numerous tall smokestacks or towers, indicating heavy industry. The city itself is largely silhouetted, with only the brightest highlights catching the sunlight. The sky is overcast with a dramatic cloud formation, partially obscuring the sun and creating a strong sense of atmospheric perspective. The foreground appears to be a densely built-up urban area with indistinct buildings. A distinct glare of sunlight reflects off the water creating a path of brightness. The overall image has a hazy, ethereal quality.",
